{"tid":1319734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 官官相衛 ] 新鴻基地產市務總監楊祖賜　獲委任輔警總監 ( 2016 )","createTime":"2019-07-15T08:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T08:50:24.000Z","uid":96894,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"62db203b5da032e7f5aa67f3123acd1be3682686","tid":1319734,"uid":96894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E6A58AE7A596E8B39C_I9ZnY_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE6A58AE7A596E8B39C_I9ZnY_1200x0.png&h=5ce2351b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9zOysiK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9zOysiK.jpg&h=8e4486a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8TEqiqC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8TEqiqC.jpg&h=fe56c34c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府今日宣布委任楊祖賜為香港輔助警察隊總監，以接替行將退休的總監姚仰龍，任命即日生效。<br />\n<br />\n楊祖賜現年58歲，是新鴻基地產發展有限公司的市務總監，曾是香港奧運射擊代表隊隊長。<br />\n<br />\n他於1989年4月加入香港輔助警察隊為輔警警員，於2004年10月晉升為輔警警司，並於2008年12月升為輔警高級警司，隨後於2010年8月升為輔警總警司。於2013年11月1日，楊祖賜獲行政長官委任為輔警副總監。<br />\n<br />\n警方指出，楊祖賜具備多方面的行動及管理經驗。於2004年，他獲頒香港輔助警察隊長期服務獎章，並於2014年獲頒第一勳扣。"},{"pid":"d5cd72de96a989e2cb15402d44e7b913b5380aeb","tid":1319734,"uid":96894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNXrNmS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNXrNmS.gif&h=a8b376c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"512db7febe6899031b40c2afc3a312eebc71205c","tid":1319734,"uid":238051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】有人冒警！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"79cb6822184b53014224965c18f63d7831d5a672","tid":1319734,"uid":96894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/msj52W6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmsj52W6.png&h=12e1bfd0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}